{"tid":1158842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人開始懷念CY ?","createTime":"2019-05-17T08:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T03:28:38.000Z","uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a54d896cd652435f10c93588a92fc5f660ebc6c","tid":1158842,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"國教   普選都係為香港好<br />\n如果有普選，上屆就選咗薯片做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家就唔會推引渡條例<br />\n<br />\n而且CY 就算點強硬，都唔會推23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e6466cc7ebf024d1531f240660dbccee986da9","tid":1158842,"uid":48362,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"你真係好撚天真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12ee763112ca7ef4014c29046fe9ba5c03a60ab","tid":1158842,"uid":68026,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"食開豬鎪突然轉糧比人質食屎 就話豬鎪好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa340f70facb7ef9e928f052c742be7b40cc15c","tid":1158842,"uid":162477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"你以為佢唔會做呢D仆街嘢？可能做得仲仆街！"},{"pid":"c3baa5aa9f264db83e1225e827c604d9c003a61f","tid":1158842,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8dc1f68aae4184544be7ab9d1fa35eb4da8c79","tid":1158842,"uid":185606,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"國教為香港好<br />\n<br />\n樓主食開屎大？"},{"pid":"127242705eac86946e77fb55b03c592bd0da084b","tid":1158842,"uid":251086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"食兩舊屎嗰時就懷念只需食一舊既時光"},{"pid":"ea64f5671ad010da0ab3265d176860a8b8cf9523","tid":1158842,"uid":191394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"樓主正宗食屎狗"},{"pid":"bb607f3af998f69bfc16ff9518b810649588033e","tid":1158842,"uid":175479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"其實會懷念係因為每個比上個都要更表忠。如果係選到薯片可能都差不多。"},{"pid":"3f63b363ca835b1fb3a4f691b6b6bf215cfbfa5d","tid":1158842,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"cf140c67bd9bf7313c7072e3218d55c5354be990","tid":1158842,"uid":9022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"有部分香港人真係好撚鐘意食屎，食屎唔洗咁大聲周圍講，引埋其他on9仔一齊食。<br />\n屌你老母見到個post 名就嬲到仆街<br />\n話撚知你假膠，去到呢啲情況仲玩呢啲"},{"pid":"f26886707d42ba839dbc103f18100c3a10c57137","tid":1158842,"uid":201721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"你咁樣不如懷念下煲呔曾<br />\n<br />\n佢除咗推高樓市之外，政治方面相比689同777都唔算乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n起碼你嗰時屌鳩完政府/上街遊行，佢成日會喺新聞講返「政府會持續聆聽市民聲音」「我哋會不斷改善」安慰下你，又搞下「形象工程」，叫下口號「我會做好呢份工」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">至少唔會好似某個人第二日就行出黎屌鳩班示威者做「暴徒」</span></strong>；<br />\n<br />\n起碼東亞運香港對日本佢有坐喺大球場嘅觀眾席支持香港隊，見到港隊入波佢會好開心慶祝，門面上又話會支持本港足壇發展（雖然無乜成效），<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但至少唔會好似某個人話體育對香港無貢獻</strong></span>；<br />\n<br />\n起碼每逢佳節佢都會拍下啲on9廣告片祝賀下市民，其實都算幾有heart 㗎喇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>至少唔會好似某個人日日喺FB 批鬥刊登蘋果日報嘅廣告商</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>煲呔曾起碼都叫做下門面功夫吖，另外兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"a01f17b9123f2a7ce240d003bbc57e5f41d09599","tid":1158842,"uid":41250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"成個政府冇一個人為香港著想，邊個做特首都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9c1e347203ee0aca0bc88de08d91747bf91db1","tid":1158842,"uid":110832,"l